name: THE FUTURE IS NOT YET DESIGNED

metadata.name: Self - Push & Pull
metadata.description:
Collaboration with Rik Oostenbroek for his 'Show Yourself' competition.

This piece focusses on the fact that we’re all multifaceted people, often with conflicting inner dialogues, opinions, desires, and goals. And that’s OK.

As much as this piece is created primarily in black and white, life isn’t black and white. Essentially this piece focusses on the push and pull of life. 

Mixed media execution.
